data.title: LO-FI SEYMOUR ASHBURY DEMO CUT
data.description: It was a very wet day up at Mt. Seymour for the 6th Annual Ashbury Demo so I decided to keep my camera dry and shoot with the iPhone. With all the weather, both phones I was using kept dying on me, so this is what we got. The day was super fun and everybody was psyched. This is snowboarding, there's nothing you can do about the weather!

data.description: The Others is a group of our close creative friends who we think represent what Ashbury is all about. Cody Comrie has been affiliated with Ashbury since the beginning, he's an old roommate, and one of the most talented Los Angeles based artists. For more about The Others: http://ashburyeyewear.com/the-others/
